"is currently enabled. PayPal payment methods are visible only to site "
"administrators and store managers. Disable this mode after testing to make "
"them available to customers."
msgstr ""
"កំពុងបើកនៅពេលនេះ។ វិធីបង់ប្រាក់ PayPal "
